  m_text: 'Step into the perspective of Elias, a third-generation regenerative

    farmer
    in the heart of the valley. As the first light touches the dew-

    covered
    fields, you will navigate the balance between traditional

    heritage and future
    sustainability. This experience highlights the

    interconnectedness of soil
    health and community resilience.'
